snippet.title: HotBunz Launch Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Buy HotBunz: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2229230/HotBunz/

HotBunz is the Ultimate Couch Multiplayer Party Game that will have you and your friends laughing until your sides hurt. This fast-paced, chaotic game is all about farting your way to victory and twerking your heart out in celebration.
